org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.meta

Class SimilarityBasedPasswordValidatorCfgDefn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.opendj.config.AbstractManagedObjectDefinition<C,S>
      • org.forgerock.opendj.config.ManagedObjectDefinition<SimilarityBasedPasswordValidatorCfgClient,SimilarityBasedPasswordValidatorCfg>
        • org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.meta.SimilarityBasedPasswordValidatorCfgDefn

  • public final class SimilarityBasedPasswordValidatorCfgDefn
extends ManagedObjectDefinition<SimilarityBasedPasswordValidatorCfgClient,SimilarityBasedPasswordValidatorCfg>
    An interface for querying the Similarity Based Password Validator managed object definition meta information.

    The Similarity Based Password Validator determines whether a proposed password is acceptable by measuring how similar it is to the user's current password.
